{"tid":1162472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商經局局長邱騰華於亞太經合組織部長級會議不點名批評美國沒尊重國際貿易在透明、非歧視性的規則下進行的理念","createTime":"2019-05-20T01:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T07:28:18.000Z","uid":82640,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"03b83351e4bae6e3f12aa43734c9f579a27da4b7","tid":1162472,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:45:33.000Z","msg":"// 他說：「確保國際貿易在透明、非歧視性的規則下進行，並讓世貿成員透過世貿的既有機制解決爭端，至為重要。亞太經合組織應重申其強化及捍衛多邊貿易制度的承諾。香港支持發表貿易部長聲明，重申亞太經合組織對維護以規則為本的制度具堅定的決心。」 //<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201905/18/P2019051800219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201905%2F18%2FP2019051800219.htm&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1yvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=41abfca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201905/18/P2019051800219.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n唉我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你下年有得去先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人將至死，講嘢都仲係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78d6bf8491abf21dfe48d5bf2a4fc7ef95ed2b9","tid":1162472,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"扯線公仔"},{"pid":"a5057b707844d6a2d05f1e2c580038152700f480","tid":1162472,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a78d6bf8491abf21dfe48d5bf2a4fc7ef95ed2b9","tid":1162472,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"扯線公仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:28:42.000Z","msg":"人黎架<br />\n用下腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6066b49c3971d5352342a3953cfd2eecf6844c2","tid":1162472,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"兜個圈話返自己"},{"pid":"164df383e83c2cb51eb1d39c8e371b0c075ada6d","tid":1162472,"uid":7369,"like":4,"di